    <refsection id="Description_ESELECT_f">
        <title>Description</title>
        <para>
            Special block similar to If-Then-Else. Input and output are synchronized.
            The incoming event is directed to one of the output event ports depending
            on the value of the regular input.
        </para>
        <para>
            For example, when the input value is between 0 and 1, the control input is redirected to the first command output; when the input value is between 1 and 2, the control input is redirected to the second command output; et c√¶tera...
        </para>
    </refsection>
